headline: 3 Ultra-High Yield Dividend Stocks Retirees Should Consider for 2025
summary: Dividend stocks can be your best friend in retirement -- especially when their payouts allow you to cover your living expenses without selling shares.  The company has grown its earnings at a 4.4% annualized pace over the past five years, and analysts estimate it will grow them by 3.5% annually over the next three to five years.
